divs: sighting detailscluster of orbs with very bright yellow lights. i first thought it was a helicopter but it had no noise or navigation lights.object was on a striaght line path roughly 500 to 700 feet high and roughly 1\4 mile away traveling sw to ne. response from other witnesses was dissmissal to curious excitment until it moved out of sight.
